name: testDeleteItemFromSideMenu
description: Verify that the Folder can be deleted with the 'Delete' button from side menu on the Project page
descriptionHtml: Verify that the Folder can be deleted with the 'Delete' button from side menu on the Project page

testStage.description: Verify that the Folder can be deleted with the 'Delete' button from side menu on the Project page

steps.name: Click on 'New Item' in the side menu
Click 'Save' button on the BaseConfigPage page
Click 'Logo' button and move to main page
Click on the 'Delete Job' link on the Folder page and go to Main Page
Click on the 'Yes' button on the DeletePage
Check if 'Welcome' is displayed on Main page
